data.description: Now available on the market is a fully turnkey 1,188 SqFt home, residing privately on 1.5 acres of land in Little Falls! The home’s combination of quality, amenity, & location make this the perfect option on the market for prospective buyers seeking a move-in ready property to raise a family in. The 3-bedroom home sits on a beautiful lot providing high appeal with a flawless structural appearance, landscaping ability, an in-ground pool with space to host family & friends, and a large garage; offering 6 parking spaces as well as workshop space & a car lift! The 1st floor of the home holds a meticulous kitchen lit up by natural & recessed lighting, a large living room, a formal dining room, a common area with attached dining space, and a bridge room connected to the 1st floor full bathroom. The 2nd floor holds the 3 spacious bedrooms, as well as the 2nd full bathroom. The full basement is renovated to provide living or common space, also suitable for additional storage!
